object.name: policystats
object.customQuery:
select count(distinct concat(policyNumber,PolicyVersion)) 
as PolicyStats_Count from policystats
object.label: policystats

object.name: claim
object.customQuery: select count(distinct claimnumber) as Claim_Count from claim where TypeCd='Claim' and cmmcontainer='Claim'
object.label: claim

object.name: basicpolicy
object.customQuery: select count(distinct concat(policyNumber,PolicyVersion)) as Policy_Count from basicpolicy where cmmcontainer='Policy'
object.label: basicpolicy

object.name: claimstats
object.customQuery: Select count(distinct claimnumber) as ClaimStats_Count from claimstats
object.label: claimstats
